{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/Animated_keyart.gif?t=1740007307\" /><strong><i>Join unique player-made taverns  or craft your own to host friends and fellow adventurers. </i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/Door.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Freedom To Create</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Express yourself</strong> in a variety of ways: <strong>painting, writing, cooking, playing instruments</strong> (with MIDI support), and <strong>customizing the environment.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/play_music.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Voice Chat!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Communicate vocally with other players in fun and interactive ways. Organize stand-up comedy nights or just spend the night with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/Knife_fail.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Interact with everything</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a new level of interactivity with <strong>physics</strong>. <strong>Throw</strong>, <strong>flip</strong>, <strong>eat</strong>, <strong>drink</strong>, <strong>pose</strong>, <strong>pick up</strong> and much more\u2026 every object can be used in various ways, often with unexpected results.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/explosion.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Games &amp; Activities</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Participate in a variety of games and social activities, making every session unique. From classic tavern games to hosting themed events, Taverna is an ideal space for role-play gatherings.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/chess.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Immersive Environment</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a cozy, fantasy tavern straight out of your favorite story or video game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/fireplace.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customize your fantasy character</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from different fantasy races like <strong>human</strong>, <strong>orc</strong>, <strong>dwarf</strong>, or <strong>elf </strong>each with traits that slightly alter gameplay. Customize your look with clothing, accessories, and personal touches to make every character unique.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/drink.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Pick a role!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choose from between more than <strong>15 roles</strong>. Whether you decide to be a <strong>cook</strong>, a <strong>bard</strong>, or simply a <strong>traveler</strong>, this choice will shape your experience in Taverna, influencing interactions and adding replayability to each session.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/buy_a_beer.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customize your tavern</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Paint </strong>walls, <strong>add plants</strong>, <strong>lights</strong>, and <strong>decorations </strong>to create a unique atmosphere. Every detail in your tavern is yours to customize, making it a welcoming place for friends and fellow adventurers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/Posing.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Cook like a chef!</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix and match a variety of ingredients, not just food! Create unique items and add a personal touch to your tavern gatherings, expanding the possibilities of what you can offer to guests.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/cheese.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Gold coins and progression</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Earn gold and use it to <strong>unlock unique items </strong>to progress your tavern. <strong>Chairs</strong>, <strong>pots</strong>, <strong>books</strong>, <strong>cutlery</strong>, <strong>ingredients</strong>, <strong>paints </strong>and so much more</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/extras/book_02.gif?t=1740007307\" /></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3219160?t=1740007307","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1740007307","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/2574594eb09fee536972faac134ad38e983b5561/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1740007307","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219160/2574594eb09fee536972faac134ad38e983b5561/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1740007307","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"PvP","id":49},{"description":"Online PvP","id":3